09:14.087 --> 09:16.189
HARRISON: I think
we're taking slow strides,

09:16.223 --> 09:18.291
but you have to believe
things are getting better,

09:18.325 --> 09:20.427
otherwise,
you'll just die inside.

09:20.460 --> 09:22.129
Is there anything
you'd like to say to

09:22.162 --> 09:24.231
other black kids out there
who may be going through

09:24.264 --> 09:25.933
the same thing?

09:25.966 --> 09:27.234
Just be you.

09:27.267 --> 09:29.069
At all costs.

09:29.102 --> 09:30.738
But also,

09:30.771 --> 09:33.306
stop dressing so crazy.

09:33.340 --> 09:34.775
Hmm.

