11:55.315 --> 11:57.017
Well, your news
is problematic.

11:57.050 --> 11:58.852
-Bitch, that ain't my fault!
-Whoa, whoa, whoa!

11:58.886 --> 12:00.453
I won't have you on my show
calling anyone "bitches."

12:00.487 --> 12:01.855
How you gonna blame me
for news being bad, huh?

12:01.889 --> 12:03.356
FRANKLIN: All right,
simmer down, simmer down.

12:03.390 --> 12:04.758
You can't even have
an intelligent dialogue

12:04.792 --> 12:06.559
-without spewing profanities.
-(groans)

12:06.593 --> 12:07.961
-It's--it's ludicrous.
FRANKLIN: Okay, okay, okay.

12:07.995 --> 12:11.064
Paper Boi,
isn't a lack of a father

12:11.098 --> 12:13.233
the reason you hate transpeople?

12:13.266 --> 12:14.634
What?
Lack of a father?

12:14.667 --> 12:16.436
Man, you hear yourself?
(bleep), shut up.

12:16.469 --> 12:17.737
Man, here's the thing.

12:17.771 --> 12:19.472
Man, I--
it's hard for me to care

12:19.506 --> 12:21.241
about this when nobody
cares about me

12:21.274 --> 12:23.043
as a black human man,
you feel me?

12:23.076 --> 12:24.812
Like, Caitlyn Jenner
is just doing

12:24.845 --> 12:26.446
what rich white men been doing
since the dawn of time,

12:26.479 --> 12:28.081
which is whatever
the hell he want.

12:28.115 --> 12:30.750
So why should I care?
What make him so special?

12:30.784 --> 12:32.452
But--but as a black man
in this country,

12:32.485 --> 12:34.621
shouldn't you care about
the civil liberties of others,

12:34.654 --> 12:36.089
since they're
so closely related to--to

12:36.123 --> 12:37.490
your struggle for equality?

12:37.524 --> 12:39.292
What you talking 'bout?
I do care.

12:39.326 --> 12:41.228
Look, I don't have a problem
with gay people, transpeople,

12:41.261 --> 12:42.896
because that's tolerance,
but where's tolerance

12:42.930 --> 12:45.298
for people like me?
You know what I'm saying?

12:45.332 --> 12:48.735
Like...
(sighs) Look.

12:48.768 --> 12:50.637
I should be able
to say something is weird

12:50.670 --> 12:52.505
without people hating on me.
All right?

12:52.539 --> 12:55.308
Look, I never--
I never said anything

12:55.342 --> 12:56.743
about taking away
nobody's rights.

12:56.776 --> 12:58.011
A'ight? Never.

12:58.045 --> 12:59.479
I--I understand
what you're saying,

12:59.512 --> 13:01.849
but--but some people
found your remarks offensive.

13:01.882 --> 13:04.818
Yeah, well,
freedom of speech, (bleep).

13:06.053 --> 13:08.455
No, you're right.

13:08.488 --> 13:09.990
I agree.

13:15.028 --> 13:19.132
But your music is detrimental
to black teens.

13:19.166 --> 13:22.335
(scoffs) Yeah, but so is
all rap music, right?

13:22.369 --> 13:23.636
-I mean, and rock music...
-Rock.

13:23.670 --> 13:24.972
Before it was
taken over by rap.

13:25.005 --> 13:27.007
Yeah, I agree.

